We talked with you about three chiefs of the strategic management schools.

27:24.000 --> 27:28.000
We talked about the pre-schools.

27:28.000 --> 27:32.000
Now let's talk about the descriptive schools.

27:32.000 --> 27:33.000
There are more of them.

27:33.000 --> 27:45.000
This is the school of entrepreneurship, this is the cognitive school, the school of education, the school of power, the school of culture or cultural school, the school of the external environment and the school of configuration.

27:45.000 --> 27:49.000
Each of them has several words.

27:49.000 --> 27:54.000
These are the main positions that characterize these schools.

27:54.000 --> 28:05.000
Please note that these schools began to appear in the 1960s, but their development began after the 1980s.

28:05.000 --> 28:10.000
The main peak of development occurs after the 1990s.

28:10.000 --> 28:13.000
So, in order, the school of entrepreneurship.

28:13.000 --> 28:17.000
The main prerequisites of the school of entrepreneurship are as follows.

28:17.000 --> 28:22.000
The strategy exists in the mind of the leader.

28:22.000 --> 28:25.000
He understands what the future is.

28:25.000 --> 28:30.000
He intuitively chooses the direction of movement.

28:30.000 --> 28:34.000
He foresees the future of the organization.

28:34.000 --> 28:37.000
Therefore, the main emphasis is on foreseeing.

28:37.000 --> 28:43.000
The process of forming a strategy can be called semi-conscious.

28:43.000 --> 28:49.000
It is based on intuition, on the life experience of the company's leader.

28:50.000 --> 29:02.000
It does not matter whether this strategy is born in the head of the leader or he perceives this strategy from the outside.

29:02.000 --> 29:05.000
The leader promotes his concept.

29:05.000 --> 29:09.000
He personally controls its implementation.

29:09.000 --> 29:18.000
He personally makes timely adjustments in the implementation of the strategy.

29:18.000 --> 29:28.000
Therefore, for strategic foreseeing within the framework of the school of entrepreneurship, we lay down a certain flexibility.

29:28.000 --> 29:37.000
Thus, it turns out that the entrepreneurial strategy is both well-thought-out,

29:37.000 --> 29:44.000
and, from the point of view of a holistic concept, is developing,

29:44.000 --> 29:51.000
since the details are determined by the company's leader.

29:51.000 --> 29:56.000
The entrepreneurial organization is distinguished by flexibility,

29:56.000 --> 30:05.000
since it is relatively simple, fast, and clearly responds to the instructions of the structure's leader.

30:06.000 --> 30:08.000
What can it be?

30:08.000 --> 30:14.000
It is a startup, a company with one owner,

30:14.000 --> 30:24.000
and it reacts quickly to the offer and instructions of this owner for any changes.

30:24.000 --> 30:28.000
On the other hand, it can be a large company,

30:28.000 --> 30:34.000
in which procedures and power relations are strictly prescribed.

30:35.000 --> 30:42.000
And in which the leader, the guru of freedom of maneuver, is left.

30:44.000 --> 30:50.000
It should be noted that the entrepreneurial strategy is difficult to find.

