01:33:51.000 --> 01:33:59.000
Business strategy is responsible for the company's managers,

01:33:59.000 --> 01:34:02.000
for the enterprise that is part of the corporation.

01:34:02.000 --> 01:34:08.000
Functional strategies are developed by the managers of the companies.

01:34:08.000 --> 01:34:15.000
These are strategies in the area of production, marketing, finance, personnel, etc.

01:34:15.000 --> 01:34:21.000
Operational strategies are responsible for the managers of the companies,

01:34:21.000 --> 01:34:25.000
managers of production, territorial managers,

01:34:25.000 --> 01:34:29.000
when they develop regions and areas.

01:34:29.000 --> 01:34:41.000
And if we talk about the events that are supposed to take place at each level of the strategy,

01:34:41.000 --> 01:34:49.000
corporate strategy is characterized by events related to the creation and management

01:34:49.000 --> 01:34:55.000
of high-productive corporate structure portfolio.

01:34:55.000 --> 01:35:00.000
It is acquisition of companies, strengthening of existing business positions,

01:35:00.000 --> 01:35:05.000
liquidation of company activities, reorganization of the company,

01:35:06.000 --> 01:35:13.000
achieving synergy due to the interaction of various business units

01:35:13.000 --> 01:35:16.000
or various structural divisions in the company,

01:35:16.000 --> 01:35:22.000
turning the presence of this synergy into a competitive advantage, its use,

01:35:22.000 --> 01:35:26.000
establishing certain investment priorities,

01:35:26.000 --> 01:35:33.000
directing corporate resources to one or another area of company development,

01:35:34.000 --> 01:35:43.000
Business strategy is characterized by events related to the development of measures

01:35:43.000 --> 01:35:49.000
aimed at strengthening the company's competitiveness,

01:35:49.000 --> 01:35:52.000
at preserving its competitive advantages,

01:35:52.000 --> 01:35:58.000
at the formation of a mechanism of reaction to certain external changes that the company faces,

01:35:59.000 --> 01:36:11.000
at strengthening and efforts to solve specific and important issues or problems of the companies that are included in the group.

01:36:11.000 --> 01:36:20.000
Functional strategy is characterized by events related to the support of business strategy,

01:36:20.000 --> 01:36:28.000
the achievement of the goals of the functional division aimed at supporting business strategy,

01:36:28.000 --> 01:36:33.000
and finally, operational strategy.

01:36:33.000 --> 01:36:43.000
These are actions to solve narrow-special issues and problems related to the achievement of the goals of a specific division.

