We must define the approach to the placement of investments between areas of activity,

01:37:15.000 --> 01:37:17.000
how the company invests its funds.

01:37:17.000 --> 01:37:26.000
We must justify the decision about the refusal of a loss-making or non-attractive business,

01:37:26.000 --> 01:37:28.000
a non-profile business.

