Business strategy focuses on actions and approaches related to management,

01:38:56.000 --> 01:39:03.000
aimed at ensuring successful business activities.

01:39:03.000 --> 01:39:14.000
The essence of business strategy is to show how to conquer strong and long-term competitive positions in the market.

01:39:14.000 --> 01:39:20.000
The essence of business strategy is presented on the slide.

01:39:20.000 --> 01:39:27.000
