01:39:27.000 --> 01:39:32.000
This is a description of the main competitive approach,

01:39:32.000 --> 01:39:37.000
whether it is low costs or differentiation,

01:39:37.000 --> 01:39:40.000
again, it is necessary to specify what kind of differentiation,

01:39:40.000 --> 01:39:43.000
or it is focusing on specific market niches.

