01:41:46.000 --> 01:41:56.000
and, in fact, the functions that are assigned to the company's management.

01:41:56.000 --> 01:42:01.000
All this forms, in turn, structural links,

01:42:01.000 --> 01:42:08.000
which means that certain directions of activity are fixed behind these structural links,

01:42:08.000 --> 01:42:12.000
business functions are fixed behind these structural links,

01:42:12.000 --> 01:42:18.000
