01:42:25.000 --> 01:42:29.000
On the one hand, the model of functions is determined,

01:42:29.000 --> 01:42:33.000
on the other hand, the model of structures is determined.

01:42:33.000 --> 01:42:36.000
By applying the model of functions to the model of structures,

01:42:36.000 --> 01:42:45.000
we get a business model of organizational structure based on the company's developed strategy.

